Name: TM Proforma Options Account
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the field set that will be used to display the fields on the Scenario Options modal that are on the Account object

Name: TM Proforma Options Scenario
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the field set that will be use to display the fields on the Scenario Options modal that are on the Scenario object

Name: TM Proforma Quantity Pricing
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the field set that will be use to display the fields on the Proforma Quantity and Pricing screen

Name: TM Proforma Default Style
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the static resource name for the default styles of Proforma base page and template.

Name: TM Proforma Total Quantity Pricing
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates field-set is used to display the configurable columns in the summary row on the Proforma Quantity and Pricing screen

Name: Scenario Card Screen
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the value of the lookup_key for the Screen record used to define the Scenario Card layout

Name: 16976AAC_96E0_4096_A603_997E758E901D
LLC_BI__Description__c: When this system property is active, the loan name does not render on the Loan Facility Creation page. The value is the temporary name created for any new loan or facility. By default, it is inactive.

Name: 6FC36E5F_2345_4321_8618_30C376FA5741
LLC_BI__Description__c: This is the lookup key for the default screen utilized in additional fields.

Name: Show Setup Fee
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system property gives administrators the option to display the Setup Fee total on the Proforma Summary card. By default, the system property value is set to true, and the Setup Fee total displays on the Proforma Summary card.

Name: Enable_Data_Carryover
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system setting enables support for cross tab conditional rendering within the Treasury Maintenance experience.

Name: Write Back Blocked Objects
LLC_BI__Description__c: This property allows you to enter a comma delimited list of SObjects that will not be updated when the Treasury Maintenance write back trigger is executed. On installation, the system sets Is Active to true and the value to 'User,LLC_BI__Checklist__c'.

Name: Spreads TTM Data Update
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system property identifies when the system has executed the TTMLookupBatchUpdater and TTMRecordValueBatchUpdater batch updaters. On installation, the system sets Is Active to True and the value to True if the system has executed the batch updaters.

Name: Delete Maintenance Request Statuses
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the which statuses will cause the Delete link to display for a treasury maintenance record

Name: Delete Maintenance Order Statuses
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the which statuses will cause the Delete icon to display for a maintenance order on the Maintenance Request Orders card.

Name: Edit Maintenance Statuses
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the which statues will cause the Edit link to display for a treasury maintenance record

Name: Complete Maintenance Statuses
LLC_BI__Description__c: Enter a comma-delimited list of statuses that update the Treasury Service parameters per maintenance request.

Name: Treasury Services Summary Fieldset
LLC_BI__Description__c: Identifies the fielset to be used for the Treasury Services Summary view.

Name: Enable Custom Service Total
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system property allows you to enable the Service Total section of the proforma to be configurable.

Name: Display View Scenario Icon
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system property indicates if the View Scenario Icon should display on the Proforma scenario card.

Name: 0698A9CC_92E6_498E_8688_064298C57E11
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system property gives admins the option to include deposits/contacts already associated with a Treasury Service. By default, the system property value is set to false and deposits/contacts already associated with a Treasury Service will be excluded.

Name: OVERRIDE_All_Relationships_Field_Set
LLC_BI__Description__c: OVERRIDE FOR NON SS_PE & TIN_PE FIELDS (PDI-7501)

Name: OVERRIDE_Individuals_Field_Set
LLC_BI__Description__c: OVERRIDE FOR NON SS_PE & TIN_PE FIELDS (PDI-7501)

Name: OVERRIDE_Businesses_Field_Set
LLC_BI__Description__c: OVERRIDE FOR NON SS_PE & TIN_PE FIELDS (PDI-7501)

Name: Respondent ID
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the Financial Institutions respondent ID based on the regulating agency and type of institution.

Name: Financial Institution
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates of the name of the Financial Institution that is submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Respondent Name
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the name of the Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Respondent State
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the 2 character State code of the Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data. For example, for North Carolina enter NC.

Name: Respondent Address
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the address of the Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Respondent City
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the City of the Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Respondent Zip
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the ZIP of the Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Parent Name
LLC_BI__Description__c: If respondent is a mortgage banking subsidiary (MBS) or a non-depository institution that has an affiliation with a depository institution, this field indicates the name of the Parent Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Parent Address
LLC_BI__Description__c: If respondent is a mortgage banking subsidiary (MBS) or a non-depository institution that has an affiliation with a depository institution, this field indicates the address of the Parent Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Parent City
LLC_BI__Description__c: If respondent is a mortgage banking subsidiary (MBS) or a non-depository institution that has an affiliation with a depository institution, this field indicates the city of the Parent Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Parent State
LLC_BI__Description__c: If respondent is a mortgage banking subsidiary (MBS) or a non-depository institution that has an affiliation with a depository institution, this field indicates the 2 character state of the Parent Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Contact Fax Number
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field is the contact person's Fax number at the Financial Institution who may be contacted with questions about the Financial Institution's HMDA submission.

Name: Parent Zip
LLC_BI__Description__c: If respondent is a mortgage banking subsidiary (MBS) or a non-depository institution that has an affiliation with a depository institution, this field indicates the ZIP code of the Parent Financial Institution submitting the HMDA data.

Name: Contact Name
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field is the contact person's name at the Financial Institution who may be contacted with questions about the Financial Institution's HMDA submission.

Name: Contact Phone Number
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field is the contact person's phone number at the Financial Institution who may be contacted with questions about the Financial Institution's HMDA submission.

Name: Contact Email
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field is the contact person's Email address at the Financial Institution who may be contacted with questions about the Financial Institution's HMDA submission.

Name: Contact Street Address
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field is the contact person's Street Address at the Financial Institution who may be contacted with questions about the Financial Institution's HMDA submission.

Name: Contact City
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field is the contact person's City at the Financial Institution who may be contacted with questions about the Financial Institution's HMDA submission.

Name: Contact State
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field is the contact person's 2 character State at the Financial Institution who may be contacted with questions about the Financial Institution's HMDA submission. For example, for North Carolina enter NC.

Name: Legal Entity Identifier
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the 20 character Financial Institutions Legal Entity Identifier.

Name: Contact Zip
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field is the contact person's ZIP at the Financial Institution who may be contacted with questions about the Financial Institution's HMDA submission.

Name: Federal Agency
LLC_BI__Description__c: Enter 1 for Office of the Comptroller of the Currency, 2 for Fed Reserve System, 3 for Fed Deposit Ins Corp, 5 for National Credit Union Admin, 7 for US Dept. of Housing and Urban Development (HUD), 9 for Consumer Financial Protection Bureau (CFPB)

Name: Federal Tax ID
LLC_BI__Description__c: This field indicates the 10 character Financial Institutions Federal Tax Id.

Name: Prevent Field Map Override
LLC_BI__Description__c:
The following system property prevents the Fall 2016 GA release data installer from overwriting the field maps for three Opportunity object fields:
Product Line, Product Type, and Product. Configure this system property before running the data installers

Name: A634CA61_2905_4166_AF41_A42D33ADA887
LLC_BI__Description__c: When active and true, this system property allows analysts to group two different Spreads periods (annual and interim periods) in the output of print, export, or import analysis. By default, the system sets Is Active to true and the value to false.

Name: 206C2A91_6431_4584_9418_E3132B16C83C
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system property enables the ability to scale math (addition and subtraction) in cell. On installation, the system sets Is Active to true and the value to false.

Name: A407FE53_AE52_40C8_8860_3984396F1418
LLC_BI__Description__c: When active and a number populates the Value field, this system property allows a financial institution to determine the batch size when backfilling existing Spreads records.  By default, the system property is active and the value is 200.

Name: 217277B5_ABA1_4BB5_92EB_51F04AE13085
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system property determines which entity involvements types on loans to include within the Debt Schedule in Spreads. By default, the system sets Is Active to true and the value to a single comma (,).

Name: C4AA7243_5DB4_41F7_AE28_12BD0C58D6AD
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system property controls if a divider column displays to separate interims from annual periods when users print/export Spreads. By default, the system sets Is Active to true and the value to true.

Name: CD3D0C98_6878_4D26_8708_5855D813A92B
LLC_BI__Description__c: This system property allows Spreads and CRE Analysis users to import period values from another period. On installation, the system sets Is Active totrueand the value tofalse.

Name: 7746D7C0_8ED0_40F3_88A5_8A9FE7CF442A
LLC_BI__Description__c: When active and an email address populates the Value field, this system property allows a financial institution to determine the recipients of the Historical Math in Cell Accuracy failure email.
